’Ů@657cb086e96d8d4986140fbc12f4d86e42af4491026b36f3248aba80d0773bc9ŮéTitle: title: is-admin
Path: Examples
Content:
Return 'iamroot' if nushell is running with admin/root privileges, and 'iamnotroot' if not.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> if (is-admin) { "iamroot" } else { "iamnotroot" }
iamnotroot

```
